# Wumpus World CNF 
#   Pxy   = there is a pit in cell (x,y)
#   Bxy   = there is a breeze in cell (x,y)
#   safe22 = (2,2) is safe (no pit)
#
# World layout 
# (1,3) (2,3) (3,3)
# (1,2) (2,2) (3,2)
# (1,1) (2,1) (3,1)

# start square has no pit
-P11

# There is a pit in at least one of the squares next to it
# If there is a pit next to a square, that square will have a breeze

# If B11 is true, then at least one of P12 or P21 must be true.
-B11 P12 P21
# If P12 is true, then B11 must be true.
-P12 B11
# same
-P21 B11

# If B12 is true then one of its neighbors must contain a pit
-B12 P11 P13 P22
# If any neighbor has a pit B12 must be T
-P11 B12
-P13 B12
-P22 B12

# If B21 is true then one of these squares must have a pit
-B21 P11 P22 P31
# Each pit produces a breeze
-P11 B21
-P22 B21
-P31 B21

# (2,2) is safe if safe22 is T
-safe22 -P22
P22 safe22